==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stellion
<hw>Stel"lion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>stellio</ets> a newt having starlike spots on its back, fr.
<ets>stella</ets> a star.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A lizard
(<spn>Stellio vulgaris</spn>), common about the Eastern Mediterranean
among ruins. In color it is olive-green, shaded with black, with small
stellate spots. Called also <altname>hardim</altname>, and <altname>star
lizard</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stellionate</ent>⟦br⟧
